title: Ragga Jungle Vol 1
description:
Desert Storm Presents Ragga Jungle Volume One
=============================================

This is my first torrent - I have loads more tunes from back in the day in the UK.  This is one of the later ones from the Jungle era (1995).

This isn't available anymore so that's why I'm sharing it.  The original is in a different order mixed by Devious Dee (and includes Jungle Blanca by Faze 1 FM) but this version has split tracks.

Enjoy.
---------------------------------------------
Desert Storm would like to say big-up and thank you to all artists and record companies whose material is featured on this album.

Unity is the key - Love Life!

We would also like to say thank you to the following: "God Almighty".
